<p>The critical limitation of all WooCommerce M-Pesa plugins is third-party dependency: if a plugin is abandoned by its developer or becomes incompatible with a WordPress or WooCommerce update, payment processing breaks until the plugin is updated or replaced.</p>

<p>Kenyan businesses that have built revenue-critical operations on an outdated plugin face downtime that costs directly in lost sales.</p>

